overview:
iPad 2 Cases is an online directory created to help people discover and compare the wide variety of options to protect and cover their iPads. iPad Case Finder features cases from manufactures all over the world, and helps people find the perfect case for their individual needs.

iPad Case Finder features some of the best iPad cases on the market today. With iPad Case Finder, you can search for iPad cases by case maker, style, or just browse the site for cases. Once you find a case you like, click on it for more information, including a high-resolution photo, a detailed description of the case, pricing information, where you can purchase the case, and cases similar to the specific case youâ€™re looking at.

iPad Case Finder was started in May 2010 by Lachy Groom and Daniel Brusilovsky and is based in Palo Alto, Calif.
